<%# Global IGDB-search modal — opened by the `[+]` link on `/games`.
    2026-05-17 — the global `i` keybind that used to open this modal
    was removed in the legacy-keyboard-shortcut sweep; the bracketed
    `[+]` link in the page header is the only entry point now.
    Submits the typed query to
    `GET /games/search` (existing `GamesController#search`) which
    renders `_search_results.html.erb` inside the
    `<turbo-frame id="igdb_search_results">` below. The results
    render `[add]` for IGDB hits not yet in the local library and
    `[update]` for existing rows; `[update]` opens the shared
    overwrite-confirmation dialog (`#igdb-overwrite-modal`).
    No JS confirm/alert/prompt anywhere (CLAUDE.md hard rule).

    Phase 27 spec 04 (2026-05-17) — copy + control polish:
      - Title trimmed: "add a game from igdb" → "add a game".
      - Input placeholder trimmed: "search igdb…" → "search…".
        The "igdb" context is implied by the title now.
      - The explicit `[search]` button is GONE. The input auto-fires
        a search when the trimmed value reaches the min-chars cutoff
        (5 by default) OR when the user presses Enter at any length
        ≥ 1.
      - `[cancel]` swaps to BracketedMutedLinkComponent (muted
        secondary affordance — same primitive the session-revoke,
        Slack/Discord help, and Doorkeeper "cancel" surfaces use).
      - The inline `style="max-width: 720px;"` band-aid is gone; the
        wide modal now opts into the new `.pane-dialog--wide`
        modifier so other `.confirm-modal.pane-dialog` dialogs keep
        their 420px cap. The inner wrapper's redundant
        `width: min(720px, 92vw)` is also dropped now that the
        outer `<dialog>` sizes correctly. %>
<dialog id="igdb-search-modal"
        class="confirm-modal pane-dialog pane-dialog--wide"
        data-controller="igdb-search-modal"
        data-igdb-search-modal-url-value="<%= search_games_path %>"
        data-igdb-search-modal-min-chars-value="5"
        data-action="click->igdb-search-modal#clickOutside keydown->igdb-search-modal#keydown">
  <div class="confirm-modal-inner">
    <div class="dialog-title">add a game</div>
    <div>
      <input type="search"
             placeholder="search…"
             autocomplete="off"
             data-igdb-search-modal-target="input"
             data-action="input->igdb-search-modal#search keydown.enter->igdb-search-modal#search"
             style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 24px; padding: 0 6px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--color-text);" />
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 8px;">
      <%= turbo_frame_tag "igdb_search_results" %>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
      <%= render(BracketedMutedLinkComponent.new(
            label: "cancel",
            href: "#",
            data: { action: "click->igdb-search-modal#close" }
          )) %>
    </div>
  </div>
</dialog>
